* build step
  * create sandbox
      mkdir /path/to/sandbox/
      mkdir /path/to/sandbox/rubygems
      mkdir /path/to/sandbox/rubygems/bin
      ln -s /path/to/sandbox/rubygems/bin /path/to/sandbox/bin
  * install needed activation script
      /path/to/sandbox/bin/activate_sandbox
* user config step
    ~/.sandbox/config
    list of gems to install
    change install version choices
